  "description": {
    "zh": "那群该死的混蛋！我大概知道是谁袭击了我那辆运送M249 SAW的车队了！我手下有人跟我说看起来像是一小撮前USEC的人。我要你回海关去替我收拾他们，同时我搞清楚他们到底为什么偷我的枪。我敢打赌那些混蛋把枪藏在什么地方了。",
    "en": "Those fucking bastards! I believe I know who attacked my convoy that was carrying my shipment of the M249 SAW! One of my guys told me it looked like a small group of Ex-USEC guys. I need you to go back to Customs and take care of them for me while I figure out why the fuck they stole my guns. I bet those bastards have them stashed somewhere."
  },
